the 44th saturn awards, presented by the academy of science fiction, fantasy and horror films, honor the best science fiction, fantasy and horror films of 2004. the 44th saturn awards were held on march 21, 2005 at the universal hilton in hollywood, california. the nominees were announced on january 12, 2005 and the winners were announced on march 21, 2005. the ceremony was hosted by comedian patton oswalt. "the lord of the rings: the two towers" was the major winner at the 44th saturn awards. it won eight awards including best film and best director for peter jackson. other winners
supachai panitchpakdi (, , ; born 30 january 1948) is a thai economist and academic who served as the 12th prime minister of thailand from 5 december 2006 to 24 march 2007. supachai was born in 1948 in the town of nakhon sawan, chanthaburi province. after completing his secondary education at dusit thani school, he studied economics at chulalongkorn university, earning a phd in 1977. he then held various positions at chulalongkorn university, including acting rector from 1990 to 1991. supachai first entered thai politics in 1992, when he was elected as a member of parliament for the democrat party.
he served as deputy minister of industry and commerce from 1996 to 1997 and as deputy prime minister from 1997 to 2001. in 2001, he was appointed minister of finance by prime minister thaksin shinawatra and held that position until he was appointed prime minister in 2006. during his time as prime minister, supachai led thailand through its most difficult period since the thai revolution of 1932; the global economic recession of 2007-2008 caused severe economic problems for thailand, and supachai's government was widely criticised for its handling of the crisis. however, supachai also presided over a period of significant
the folóï oak forest is an oak forest located in the municipality of pafos, cyprus. it is one of the most important and largest oak forests in cyprus, covering an area of 38 hectares. the folóï oak forest is a protected area, and it is also a ramsar site. it is considered to be an important bird area by the international union for conservation of nature (iucn). the folóï oak forest is also a national park, and it is part of the pafos forest complex. the folóï oak forest was first mentioned in written sources in the 13th century. at
