military is a 2003 indian tamil-language film written and directed by s. shankar. it is a fictionalized account of the battle of kargil, a conflict between india and pakistan over control of kashmir. plot military is a story set during the battle of kargil between india and pakistan. the film tells the story of four soldiers: subedar gopi (nassar), private bala (jagapathi babu), havildar inder (aravind akkineni) and lieutenant colonel suresh (rajinikanth). the four soldiers are from different parts of india and have very different backgrounds. gopi is from a lower-middle-class family in tamil nadu; bala is from a poor
